The Future Forest Company are focused on fighting climate change at scale, right here in the UK. Our mission is to plant 50 million trees by 2025, creating rich ecosystems to support the recovery of our wildlife, always planting the right tree in the right place. Our expert forestry teams choose the right tree mix for every site, depending on location, soil type, elevation, and other factors. When you sponsor a tree with us, you receive a digital tree certificate with a photo of your own sapling, planted here in the UK, as well as the what3words geolocation, so you can come and visit.